Name: A Series of Temporal Mishaps
About the game: A Series of Temporal Mishaps is an ever-growing first-person platformer set in distinct eras of earth's history. Travel through time and overcome platforming obstacles to reach each era's objective...while making more than a couple mistakes along the way. Current State: Unlocked Levels 1) Primordial Sea 2) Desert Wadi 3) Abandoned Kingdom 4) Nuclear Spillway Locked Levels 5) Sunken Pyramid (unlocked August 30) -Sign up for our newsletter for early access Upcoming Level 6) TBA (releases August 30) Features: -Wide variety of landscapes set across time -Free-running elements -Platforming obstacles like sinking platforms, puzzles, and launch pads -Observe scientific phenomena and discover historical records
